dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_Addresses_2014.gdb. [Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data for this county, please visit: https://gis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
